## Third-Party Dependencies

This application uses the following open-source libraries:

### AndroidX Libraries
- **androidx.core:core-ktx** - Apache License 2.0
- **androidx.appcompat:appcompat** - Apache License 2.0
- **androidx.work:work-runtime-ktx** - Apache License 2.0
- **com.google.android.material:material** - Apache License 2.0
- **androidx.activity:activity-ktx** - Apache License 2.0

### Media & Networking
- **VLC for Android (libvlc-all)** - LGPL 2.1 or later / GPL 2.0 or later
  - https://www.videolan.org/legal.html
- **Gson** - Apache License 2.0
  - https://github.com/google/gson
- **JSch** - BSD-style license
  - https://github.com/mwiede/jsch
- **Apache HttpComponents (httpclient-android)** - Apache License 2.0
  - https://hc.apache.org/

### Testing Libraries
- **JUnit** - Eclipse Public License 1.0
- **Mockito** - MIT License
- **Espresso** - Apache License 2.0

